/wordpress-plugins-library/micropayments/?af=7789#description\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CM MicroPayments Pro</a> This AddOn for CM MicroPayment and PeepSo supports adding a virtual wallet functionality to PeepSo social network.\r\n\r\nA new tab will appear on PeepSo members profile to show user wallet and transaction history. Admin can define bonus currency or charge for posting and other PeepSo related actions. The number of points in the wallet can also be shown next to user name.\r\n\r\nMicroPayment also interacts with <a href=\"https://www.peepso.com/downloads/peepso-cmanswerspro/\">CM Answers - PeepSo Integration Plugin</a> by allowing admin to charge or grant currency for posting questions or answers\r\n\r\nThe plugin is an integration between <strong>CM MicroPayments Pro</strong> and <strong>PeepSo</strong>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Please note that this integration requires <a href=\"https://www.cminds.com/wordpress-plugins-library/micropayments/?af=7789#description\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CM MicroPayments Pro</a>.</strong>\r\n\r\n[edd-screenshots]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:81:\"https://www.peepso.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2017/01/micropayment-for-peepso.png\";s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13052;s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"Third Party\";s:4:\"slug\";s:10:\"thirdparty\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:13052;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:7;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:7:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13286;s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"addon\";s:4:\"slug\";s:5:\"addon\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:13286;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:12:\"download_tag\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:4;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13283;s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"cm\";s:4:\"slug\";s:2:\"cm\";s:10:\"te