alled and activated)</li>\r\n 	<li>Separators (These act like section headers, dividing fields into meaningful groups such as personal information, work, and education.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>An \'Add New\' button appears in the backend of your site: PeepSo &gt; Profiles allows to add new fields.</li>\r\n 	<li>Set privacy to profile fields.</li>\r\n 	<li>Reorganize profile fields to your liking.</li>\r\n 	<li>Set field validation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Set field requirements.</li>\r\n 	<li>Add more genders.</li>\r\n 	<li>And many more...</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:73:\"https://www.peepso.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2018/03/profiles_icon-2.png\";s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13363;s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"Core\";s:4:\"slug\";s:4:\"core\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:13363;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:13361;s:5:\"count\";i:9;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:13:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13083;s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"about\";s:4:\"slug\";s:5:\"about\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:13083;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:12:\"download_tag\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:1;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13091;s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"admin\";s:4:\"slug\";s:5:\"admin\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:13091;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:12:\"download_tag\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:4;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13084;s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"date\";s:4:\"slug\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:13084;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:12:\"download_tag\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:1;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:13090;s:4:\"name\";s:5